but you also finagled

24:54.326 --> 24:56.119
the fact that I have
a boyfriend named Bob.

24:56.244 --> 24:58.330
Yes, but Colleen--
She lied about--

24:58.330 --> 25:00.499
Yeah, well, that's not
the Bob that I'm sleeping with.

25:00.499 --> 25:02.667
- Uh, this is.
- What?

25:02.918 --> 25:04.836
- Hey.
- Hi, uh, Bob,

25:04.836 --> 25:07.964
this is uh, my ex,
Tommy Gavin.

25:08.089 --> 25:09.758
- Tommy, how you doing?
- Hi, how are you.

25:09.758 --> 25:11.301
J, we've got a showing
in 10 minutes.

25:11.426 --> 25:12.511
Yeah.

25:12.511 --> 25:14.971
She's taken to this job
like she was born to it.

25:14.971 --> 25:16.556
- She's a natural.
- Yeah.

25:16.681 --> 25:18.808
- Ready when you are.
- Okay, let me check my desk.

25:18.934 --> 25:20.477
Nice to meet you, Tommy.

25:20.477 --> 25:22.020
I really admire what you do.

25:22.270 --> 25:24.773
Keeping the world safe
for the rest of us schmucks.

25:24.898 --> 25:27.776
- J, 5 minutes?
- Yeah.

25:36.076 --> 25:38.411
- What'd you tell him about me?
- Don't.

25:38.411 --> 25:39.829
You know, I could--

25:39.955 --> 25:41.456
I could be wearing
a suit like that too

25:41.456 --> 25:43.166
if I wanted to spend
my money on myself,

25:43.291 --> 25:45.335
but I'd prefer
to spend my money--

25:45.460 --> 25:47.212
Our money on us.

25:47.212 --> 25:48.922
On you and me and the kids.

25:48.922 --> 25:50.215
- Here you go, okay?
- What's that?

25:50.215 --> 25:51.299
It's a credit card.

25:51.424 --> 25:53.385
- N-no, I don't want it.
- No, I want you to have this

25:53.385 --> 25:54.803
in case there's anything--

25:54.928 --> 25:56.972
- An emergency.
- No, I don't want any of Sheila's money.

25:56.972 --> 26:00.225
Does it say Sheila Keefe
on there? It says Janet Gavin, okay?

26:00.225 --> 26:02.018
It's not-- It's not
a loan, it's our money.

26:02.143 --> 26:04.104
She's over the baby thing,
the whole nine yards,

26:04.104 --> 26:06.815
- so just take it.
- What, she has no interest in Wyatt?

26:07.023 --> 26:10.694
Wyatt. Okay, we're changing
the baby's name.

26:10.819 --> 26:14.406
Did you see the reviews for
the latest Kevin Costner thing?

26:14.406 --> 26:16.741
The corporate killer
Mr. Brooks thing?

26:16.741 --> 26:18.743
His name is Wyatt. Forever.

26:18.743 --> 26:20.912
Even Bob seems to love it.

26:20.912 --> 26:24.499
Which Bob?
The short, uh, balding Bob?

26:24.499 --> 26:27.335
Or, big, tall, handsome,
I'm-banging-your-wife Bob.

26:27.460 --> 26:29.004
Huh?

26:29.004 --> 26:30.839
The thing--
His eyes, th-those are--

26:30.839 --> 26:32.173
They call them
cat's eye lenses.

26:32.299 --> 26:34.217
Chicks wear 'em, okay?
Modeling chicks.

26:34.342 --> 26:36.428
That's the first time I
ever saw a guy wear them.

26:36.428 --> 26:38.597
That's what you got.
And he's got husky-dog eyes.

26:38.597 --> 26:40.265
Ow.

26:40.265 --> 26:43.143
Go. Go. Go.

27:05.206 --> 27:06.833
- Yeah.
- Hey, what are you doing?

27:07.167 --> 27:09.461
Nothing, why?
What are you doing?

27:09.461 --> 27:11.546
Ah, the same.

27:11.546 --> 27:13.006
Oh, cool.

27:13.131 --> 27:15.216
So, you know, just, ah,
calling to check

27:15.216 --> 27:16.384
in and see
how you're doing.

27:16.509 --> 27:17.761
You all right?

27:17.886 --> 27:20.680
Uh, I don't know, man.

27:20.680 --> 27:23.350
You know, I-I sometimes--

27:23.350 --> 27:25.977
It's almost been a year now
and-- And I haven't had a drop

27:25.977 --> 27:27.646
and, yeah,
do I have a clear head?

27:27.646 --> 27:29.356
Yeah, I have a clear head.
Do I have clarity?

27:29.356 --> 27:31.858
Yeah, but, you know,
what else do I have to show for it?

27:31.858 --> 27:33.151
You know what I mean?
Nothing.

27:33.151 --> 27:34.903
What do you mean,
"nothing to show for it"?

27:35.028 --> 27:37.197
You're clean.
You're living an honest life.

27:37.197 --> 27:38.782
What are you so afraid of?

27:38.907 --> 27:40.241
I--I'm not afraid of--
Wh-What--

27:40.367 --> 27:41.951
- I'm not afraid of anything.
- Bullshit.

27:42.077 --> 27:44.079
You're waking up honest
and with clarity and with

27:44.079 --> 27:46.623
full knowledge of what you said
and you did the night before.

27:46.748 --> 27:48.124
Huh? You want to
feel the other way?

27:48.249 --> 27:49.584
I tell you what, take a hammer

27:49.584 --> 27:51.086
and hit yourself
three full good shots

27:51.086 --> 27:52.754
in the side of your head
when you wake up

27:52.754 --> 27:54.798
in the morning and see how
that feels, all right?

27:54.923 --> 27:57.050
You're right.
You know, I'm-- I'm--

27:57.050 --> 27:59.386
I'm glad you called.
I me-- I'm serious.

27:59.594 --> 28:02.055
You helped me.
You know. You're right.

28:02.055 --> 28:03.723
Yeah, not a problem.

28:03.723 --> 28:04.891
All right.

28:30.750 --> 28:32.585
- Hey.
- Hey, how you doing?

28:32.585 --> 28:36.589
Um, the knee's still really sore,
but, you know, I feel better.

28:36.589 --> 28:38.299
- A-a lot better.
- Yeah?

28:38.299 --> 28:39.676
What are you doing?

28:39.801 --> 28:42.303
Um, nothing, jus--
Just chillin'.

28:43.972 --> 28:45.432
- Doing what?
- Nothing.

28:45.640 --> 28:46.933
You're moping, aren't you?

28:46.933 --> 28:48.601
No, I-I'm not moping.

28:48.601 --> 28:51.855
Yeah, y-you're having
a giant mope fest over there, aren't you?

28:51.980 --> 28:54.816
- No, I-I was just... reading.
- You're reading.

28:54.941 --> 28:56.401
That guarantees me
that you're moping.

28:56.651 --> 28:58.194
All right? Here's what
I want you to do.

28:58.319 --> 29:00.321
When they were bringing me
down at the fire escape

29:00.321 --> 29:01.906
the other night by your place,

29:01.906 --> 29:04.075
I noticed down the block
there's a bar/caf thing.

29:04.075 --> 29:05.785
I want you to put away
the ice cream.

29:05.785 --> 29:07.662
Yeah, I know
you're eating ice cream, yeah.

29:07.787 --> 29:09.330
That which guarantees again, moping.

29:09.456 --> 29:10.832
I want you to put on
something nice,

29:10.957 --> 29:13.126
go down there a-and meet
somebody. All right?

29:13.126 --> 29:14.210
Preferably a girl.

29:14.335 --> 29:16.671
I-I got another call coming in.

29:16.796 --> 29:18.089
Bye.

29:18.089 --> 29:19.340
Yeah?

29:19.340 --> 29:20.842
You busy tonight?

29:20.967 --> 29:23.470
I'm working at the fire house.

29:23.678 --> 29:25.430
- Why?
- Literally?

29:25.680 --> 29:27.891
I only need you
for about three minutes.

29:28.016 --> 29:31.186
Yeah, well, I know but it'll
take me 45 to get over there

29:31.186 --> 29:33.772
and another 45 to get back.
I really-- I can't do it.

29:33.772 --> 29:35.857
Can I take a rain check?

29:38.067 --> 29:39.444
Egh.

29:41.446 --> 29:42.739
All right, pal.

29:43.364 --> 29:44.783
Here.

29:46.201 --> 29:47.285
Here, ready?

29:48.703 --> 29:50.330
Ready?

29:50.330 --> 29:52.123
I want you to fetch, all right?

29:53.041 --> 29:55.043
Fetch, ready?
One, two, three, go.

29:56.461 --> 30:00.048
Get it. Look. Look at the ball.

30:00.173 --> 30:01.424
See the kid chasing the ball?

30:01.549 --> 30:04.135
Dogs have been doing this for ages
with their owners, pal.

30:04.135 --> 30:06.179
Thank you, appreciate it.

30:06.179 --> 30:09.849
Charlie. Charlie. Ch--

30:11.267 --> 30:12.936
Ugh, whatever.

30:13.394 --> 30:14.813
Hello?

30:14.813 --> 30:15.897
It's me.

30:16.022 --> 30:18.066
Hey, how you doing?

30:18.066 --> 30:22.153
We uh, kind of been missing
you at the family meetings.

30:22.153 --> 30:23.988
Yeah, I'll bet.

30:23.988 --> 30:25.907
Listen, I need to talk to you.

30:25.907 --> 30:28.159
Go ahead, talk away. I got
nothing but time right now.

30:28.159 --> 30:29.327
- What?
- No, no, no.

30:29.327 --> 30:31.412
- In person. Face to face.
- Why?

30:31.412 --> 30:33.957
Because I'm your
goddamn father, that's why.

30:34.165 --> 30:36.167
- Meet me at Hanrahan's.
- The bar?

30:36.292 --> 30:38.378
No. The synagogue.

30:38.378 --> 30:41.548
Asshole. Be here within
an hour and come alone.

30:41.881 --> 30:45.260
All right, nice talking to you.

30:45.385 --> 30:46.553
Hey, what do you got?

30:46.761 --> 30:48.346
Hey. Come here.

30:48.346 --> 30:50.890
Oh, Jesus. Egh.

30:51.891 --> 30:54.477
Well, it's a start.

30:54.477 --> 30:58.064
Come on. Drop it.
Drop it. Drop it.

30:58.565 --> 30:59.858
Drop it.

31:07.073 --> 31:08.658
You quit drinking?

31:09.033 --> 31:12.704
Shh, shh, shh.
It's between me and you, huh?

31:12.704 --> 31:13.872
Yeah, I know.

31:14.747 --> 31:15.999
Ten days now.

31:15.999 --> 31:19.002
And you decide to quit
while you're sitting,

31:19.002 --> 31:21.588
every day apparently,
here in Hanrahan's bar?

31:21.588 --> 31:23.923
Three feet away
from every conceivable

31:23.923 --> 31:25.133
imaginable type of booze?

31:25.133 --> 31:27.886
You sit here all day drinking
coffee and tea and this is how--

31:28.011 --> 31:29.178
How you test yourself?

31:29.304 --> 31:31.139
You gotta face
your fears, kid.

31:31.139 --> 31:32.807
Look them straight in the eye.

31:32.932 --> 31:36.769
I spent 60 some odd years
belting down the booze.

31:36.769 --> 31:40.815
I might as well try
my last 15 or so sober.

31:40.815 --> 31:42.483
See what it's like.

31:42.609 --> 31:45.111
You're planning on living to be, like,
97 years old?

31:45.111 --> 31:46.362
Why not?

31:46.362 --> 31:49.240
- My dad did.
- Uh-huh.

31:49.240 --> 31:52.410
Listen. I'm doing this my way.

31:52.410 --> 31:55.204
So... why did you
ask me down here?

31:55.330 --> 31:57.206
I want you to tell me
about what you guys

31:57.332 --> 31:59.208
are talking about
in the meeting, you know?

31:59.334 --> 32:02.378
Just so I can you, know,
kind of, like, compare notes.

32:02.503 --> 32:06.925
We're talking about God.

32:06.925 --> 32:08.509
God?

32:08.509 --> 32:10.595
Yeah, you know. Faith.

32:10.595 --> 32:12.221
Christ.

32:12.221 --> 32:14.891
Yeah, well, I know how you
feel about those two.

32:14.891 --> 32:16.893
The great all powerful God.

32:16.893 --> 32:20.104
Where was God when I landed
on a beach in Normandy and

32:20.229 --> 32:22.607
every other guy was
getting his head blown off?

32:22.607 --> 32:24.817
When I had to fight off
those five Nazis.

32:24.817 --> 32:27.737
Fighting for my life with
only a rock in my bare hands?

32:27.737 --> 32:29.739
Where was God then, huh?

32:29.739 --> 32:31.824
Don't talk to me about God.

32:31.824 --> 32:35.036
As far as I'm concerned,
God was your mother.

32:35.036 --> 32:38.831
The way she raise you kids,
the love she showed you.

32:38.831 --> 32:41.250
The way she helped you
overcome all the stuff

32:41.250 --> 32:43.252
that scared
the shit out of you.

32:43.252 --> 32:45.380
The height thing,
the bee thing,

32:45.546 --> 32:47.298
your mother was a saint.

32:47.548 --> 32:49.801
What heights thing?
I'm not afraid of heights.

32:49.801 --> 32:51.302
What are you talking about?

32:51.302 --> 32:53.346
I'm a goddamn fireman
for Christ's sake.

32:53.346 --> 32:55.890
I'm up on the ladder or in the
bucket every other goddamn day.

32:56.015 --> 32:57.058
No, not now. Thanks to her.

32:57.058 --> 32:59.936
Christ, she couldn't even
put you in the highchair.

32:59.936 --> 33:01.521
But sh-she cured you.

33:01.521 --> 33:04.148
She took you up on the roof,
and held you over the side

33:04.148 --> 33:06.401
and tickled you with her nose.

33:06.401 --> 33:08.695
Next thing you know,
you were begging her

33:08.695 --> 33:10.321
to throw you up in the air.

33:10.321 --> 33:11.739
What was the bee thing?

33:11.739 --> 33:13.574
You were
deathly afraid of them.

33:13.700 --> 33:16.077
You used to wear
a wool hat in the summer

33:16.077 --> 33:17.787
so they wouldn't
bite you on the head.

33:17.912 --> 33:19.414
I don't think
you ever got over that.

33:19.539 --> 33:21.833
- Oh, there's one now.
- Where?

33:23.042 --> 33:24.335
Gotcha.

34:15.428 --> 34:16.596
Hello?

34:16.596 --> 34:18.639
- Hello.
- Shh.

34:18.765 --> 34:20.349
Wh-Why do I
gotta be quiet for?

34:24.479 --> 34:25.480
Hang on.

34:31.819 --> 34:33.404
Done, okay.

34:33.404 --> 34:34.989
Now I can talk.

34:35.198 --> 34:36.866
I was just wondering
what's up with Elvis.

34:36.991 --> 34:38.451
You know,
c-can I tell you one thing?

34:38.451 --> 34:41.329
The Elvis thing,
that name has to go. Okay?

34:41.454 --> 34:43.539
Because-- I mean, by the time
he gets to high school,

34:43.664 --> 34:45.541
kids are gonna
be dropping drugs at his feet

34:45.666 --> 34:47.835
and peanut butter--
Fried peanut butter sandwiches.

34:47.960 --> 34:50.171
- Okay?
- Elvis is evergreen, asshole.

34:50.296 --> 34:52.256
It's like Jesus.
It's a sacred name.

34:52.256 --> 34:55.510
It's not like Jesus.
It's nothing like Jesus.

34:55.635 --> 34:57.512
I-I got the baby coming
back in a couple of days

34:57.512 --> 34:59.680
and then basically it's just
you and me sharing him.

34:59.806 --> 35:01.349
Yay.

35:01.349 --> 35:04.894
Yeah. By the way, you, uh--
What floor are you on now?

35:05.019 --> 35:06.187
I live on the Fifth floor, why?

35:06.187 --> 35:07.355
What about w-window guards?

35:07.480 --> 35:10.024
You got window guards
and things out there on t-the terrace?

35:10.274 --> 35:11.526
The kid can barely sit up.

35:11.651 --> 35:13.402
How's he going to make
it out to the terrace?

35:13.528 --> 35:14.779
All right,
he starts sitting up.

35:14.779 --> 35:16.906
Next thing you know he sees
a bird he wants to touch

35:17.031 --> 35:19.408
and he goes out there,
seconds later he's bouncing off

35:19.534 --> 35:20.535
the roof of a taxi, okay?

35:20.535 --> 35:22.537
Eric Clapton's kid?
Does that ring a bell, huh?

35:22.662 --> 35:24.914
Oh, okay. Well,
I'll get some window guards.

35:25.039 --> 35:26.457
You're sure it's the fifth floor

35:26.457 --> 35:28.668
because it seemed awfully
much higher than that

35:28.668 --> 35:30.002
the last time I was there.

35:30.002 --> 35:32.755
I think I know
what floor I live on, you big dipshit.

35:32.755 --> 35:34.632
Anywho, so day after tomorrow?

35:34.632 --> 35:35.967
Yeah, yeah.

35:35.967 --> 35:37.343
I'm so excited, I can't wait.

35:37.343 --> 35:39.470
All right, I'll talk to you later. Bye.

35:39.470 --> 35:41.556
Jesus Christ. Unbelievable.

35:41.556 --> 35:43.349
Bless me father
for I have sinned.

35:43.349 --> 35:45.393
It has been three days
since my last confession.

35:45.393 --> 35:47.145
These are my sins.

35:49.188 --> 35:50.439
Um...

35:51.858 --> 35:54.402
I took the name
of the lord in vain 67 times.

35:54.402 --> 35:57.113
I was envious of my neighbor Shirley
and her new boyfriend, Sal.

35:57.238 --> 35:59.907
I stole the newspaper from
Shirley's doorstep one morning

35:59.907 --> 36:02.410
and I had impure thoughts
while I was watching

36:02.410 --> 36:04.745
last week's episode
of <i>According to Jim.</i>

36:06.873 --> 36:08.708
Father?

36:09.375 --> 36:11.169
I'm sorry.

36:12.086 --> 36:14.672
I won't watch
that show any more.

36:14.672 --> 36:17.216
Well, um, no--

36:17.216 --> 36:20.428
God wants you to watch the--

36:20.428 --> 36:23.639
I don't think
he cares about t-the show.

36:23.639 --> 36:25.433
I think you should, uh--

36:26.100 --> 36:28.102
Just cut down on t-the name

36:28.311 --> 36:31.230
in vain thing and the stealing thing
is probably not a good idea

36:31.230 --> 36:32.315
And uh...

36:35.067 --> 36:38.696
just, you know, say, um--
Say, um, the Hail Mary.

36:38.696 --> 36:40.448
I think th--
Say, uh, one Hail Mary.

36:41.782 --> 36:43.784
Actually, just say
the last part of the Hail Mary.

36:43.910 --> 36:45.578
The last couple of lines
of the Hail Mary.

36:45.578 --> 36:47.246
Holy Mary, Mother of God.

36:47.246 --> 36:50.625
Pray for us sinners now
and at the hour of our death, amen.

36:50.750 --> 36:52.251
At the hour of our death. Shit.

36:52.251 --> 36:54.045
- What?
- What?

36:54.545 --> 36:57.048
- Huh?
- W-What?

36:57.048 --> 37:01.010
Huh? Um, you're all set.

37:01.969 --> 37:03.262
- That's it?
- Yep.

37:03.262 --> 37:05.264
That's, uh, total ab--
Absolution.

37:05.264 --> 37:06.724
Stay away from the name thing

37:06.724 --> 37:09.685
and the stealing thing
and you'll be... golden.

37:10.770 --> 37:12.396
- Amen.
- All right, see you.

37:20.947 --> 37:22.573
Oh, uh, the, uh--

37:23.783 --> 37:25.451
It's broke.

37:55.940 --> 37:57.233
Ugh.

38:04.407 --> 38:05.408
Ahh.

