38:13.958 --> 38:15.835
<i>Nice spin move by Curry.</i>

38:15.835 --> 38:18.587
<i>Stops at about 8--
And puts it in...</i>

38:18.587 --> 38:20.172
Ah.

38:53.664 --> 38:55.958
<i>...New York up by 12.</i>

38:55.958 --> 38:58.085
<i>Daniels brings
it in for Washington...</i>

38:58.085 --> 39:00.296
<i>Needs some help...
crosses half court...</i>

39:00.296 --> 39:02.465
<i>...stops at
the three point line,</i>

39:02.465 --> 39:05.051
<i>looks to his left,
finds Butler in the quarter...</i>

39:15.144 --> 39:16.520
Buy me a drink.

39:24.528 --> 39:25.946
Yeah.

39:27.031 --> 39:28.032
Totally. What--

39:28.032 --> 39:29.408
What are you drinking?

39:29.408 --> 39:30.701
I'm having a bourbon.

39:30.701 --> 39:31.911
- Bourbon, okay.
- Mm-hmm.

39:33.746 --> 39:34.955
Hey, I'm--

39:35.081 --> 39:37.708
- I'm sorry, bartender.
- Yeah?

39:37.708 --> 39:41.253
Could I get
