39:51.639 --> 39:53.766
You have really soulful eyes.

39:55.184 --> 39:56.185
Thanks.

39:58.979 --> 40:00.981
Ah, well, what do you think of me?

40:00.981 --> 40:05.194
Oh, y-you... you're slamming.

40:05.444 --> 40:08.823
- Yeah?
- Yeah. You're totally hot.

40:08.948 --> 40:10.574
Well, thank you, sweetie pie.

40:14.995 --> 40:18.249
How'd you like to get in on
a little mother-daughter action?

40:19.500 --> 40:20.918
Wow.

40:27.508 --> 40:28.551
Let's go.

40:30.094 --> 40:32.054
<i>...Daniels gets free...</i>

40:34.723 --> 40:36.725
<i>...puts it up
and gets blocked by...</i>

40:36.725 --> 40:38.227
Agh.

40:38.352 --> 40:40.521
<i>...that's okay.
Washington gets it back...</i>

